-russias-largest-social-network/|title=Meet Telegram, A Secure Messaging App From The Founders Of VK, Russia’s Largest Social Network - TechCrunch|first=Catherine|last=Shu|publisher=|accessdate=2018-04-18|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126020419/http://techcrunch.com/2013/10/27/meet-telegram-a-secure-messaging-app-from-the-founders-of-vk-russias-largest-social-network/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2013/10/27/meet-telegram-a-secure-messaging-app-from-the-founders-of-vk-russias-largest-social-network/|title=Meet Telegram, A Secure Messaging App From The Founders O VK, Russia’s Largest Social Network - TechCrunch|first=Catherine|last=Shu|publisher=|access-date=2021-12-08|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126020419/http://techcrunch.com/2013/10/27/meet-telegram-a-secure-messaging-app-from-the-founders-of-vk-russias-largest-social-network/}}</ref>，是社交網站 VK 的技術總監。<ref name="test" />

