2017年，他被选为代表芬兰加入世界经济论坛（WEF）全球青年领袖。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=ExoAtlet CEO Ekaterina Bereziy named Young Global Leader by World Economic Forum|url=https://old.sk.ru/news/b/news/archive/2017/03/16/exoatlet-ceo-ekaterina-bereziy-named-young-global-leader-by-world-economic-forum.aspx|accessdate=2020-06-25|work=Skolkovo Community|language=en|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517145313/http://sk.ru/news/b/news/archive/2017/03/16/exoatlet-ceo-ekaterina-bereziy-named-young-global-leader-by-world-economic-forum.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Community|url=https://www.younggloballeaders.org/community/|accessdate=2020-06-25|work=The Forum of Young Global Leaders|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190319191541/http://widgets.weforum.org/ygl-2015/04.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

